title: NFL ATL: Super Bowl non-contenders
itunes:title: NFL ATL: Super Bowl non-contenders
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest NFL news including cornerback Brandon Flowers' release from the Kansas City Chiefs, Vernon Davis' plan to hold out and more. Plus, the guys decide which teams realistically have no shot at winning the Super Bowl next season.
